Installation


Install WAHVectors.jl using the julia package manager.


Since this package is pre-alpha, you will need to use the 
Pkg.clone
 method instead of the 
Pkg.add
 method.


Pkg
.
clone
(
https://github.com/BioJulia/WAHVectors.jl.git
)
